quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  58,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  58,1,"Allah ne sun li uss aurat ki baat jo a pannay shohar ke maamla mein tum se takraar kar rahi hai aur Allah se faryaad kiye jati hai Allah tum dono ki guftagu sun raha hai, woh sab kuch suneney aur dekhnay wala hai"
  58,2,"tum mein se jo log apni biwion se zhar karte hain un ki biwiyan un ki maaen nahi hain, un ki maaen to wohi hain jinhon ne un ko jina hai yeh log aik sakht napasandeedah aur jhooti baat kehte hain, aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah bara maaf karne wala aur dar guzar frmane wala hai"
  58,3,"jo log apni biwion se zhar karen phir apni uss baat se rujoo karen jo unhon ne kahi thi, to qabal is ke ke dono aik dosray ko haath lagayen, aik ghulam azad karna hoga iss se tum ko nasiyaat ki jati hai, aur jo kuch tum karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
  58,4,"aur jo shakhs ghulam nah paye woh do mahinay ke pay Dur pay rozay rakhay qabal is ke ke dono aik dosray ko haath lagayen aur jo is par bhi Qadir nah ho woh ۶۰ miskeeno ko khana khilaye yeh hukum is liye diya ja raha hai ke tum Allah aur uss ke rasool par imaan lao yeh Allah ki muqarrar ki hui hade hain, aur kafiroon ke liye dard naak saza hai"
  58,5,"jo log Allah aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat karte hain woh isi terhan zaleel o khawar kar diye jayen ge jis terhan un se pehlay ke log zaleel o khawar kiye ja chuke hain hum ne saaf saaf ayaat nazil kar di hain, aur kafiroon ke liye zillat ka azaab hai"
  58,6,uss din ( yeh zillat ka azaab hona hai ) jab Allah un sab ko phir se zindah kar ke uthaye ga aur inhen bta day ga ke woh kya kuch kar ke aeye hain woh bhool gay hain magar Allah ne un sab ka kya dhara gun gun kar mehfooz kar rakha hai aur Allah aik aik cheez par Shahid hai
  58,7,"kya tum ko khabar nahi hai ke zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ka Allah ko ilm hai? kabhi aisa nahi hota ke teen admion mein koi sargoshi ho aur un ke darmain choutha Allah nah ho, ya paanch admion mein sargoshi ho aur un ke andar chhata Allah nah ho khufia baat karne wala khuwa iss se kam hon ya ziyada, jahan kahin bhi woh hon, Allah un ke sath hota hai phir qayamat ke roz woh un ko bta day ga ke unhon ne kya kuch kya hai Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai"
  58,8,"kya tum ne dekha nahi unn logon ko jinhein sargoshian karne se mana kar diya gaya tha phir bhi woh wohi harkat kiye jatay hain jis se inhen mana kya gaya tha? yeh log choup choup kar aapas mein gunah aur zayad-ti aur rasool ki nafarmani ki baatein karte hain, aur jab tumahray paas atay hain to tumhe uss tareeqay se salam karte hain jis terhan Allah ne tum par salam nahi kya hai aur apne dilon mein kehte hain ke hamari inn baton par Allah hamein azaab kyun nahi deta unn ke liye jahannum hi kaafi hai usi ka woh eendhan banin ge bara hi bura injaam hai unn ka"
  58,9,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum aapas mein posheeda baat karo to gunah aur zayad-ti aur rasool ki nafarmani ki baatein nahi balkay neki aur taqwa ki baatein karo aur uss khuda se drtay raho jis ke huzoor tumhe hashar mein paish hona hai"
  58,10,"kaana phoosi to aik shaytani kaam hai, aur woh is liye ki jati hai ke imaan laane walay log uss se ranjida hon, halaank be azan khuda woh inhen kuch bhi nuqsaan nahi pouncha sakti, aur mominoun ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
  58,11,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum se kaha jaye ke apni mjlson mein kushadgi peda karo to jagah kushadah kar diya karo, Allah tumhe kushadgi bakhshay ga aur jab tum se kaha jaye ke uth jao to uth jaya karo tum mein se jo log imaan rakhnay walay hain aur jin ko ilm bakhsha gaya hai, Allah un ko buland darjay ataa farmaiye ga, aur jo kuch tum karte ho Allah ko is ki khabar hai"
  58,12,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jab tum rasool se takhlia mein baat karo to baat karne se pehlay kuch sadqa do yeh tumahray liye behtar aur pakeeza tar hai Albata agar tum sadqa dainay ke liye kuch nah pao to Allah ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  58,13,"kya tum dar gay is baat se ke takhlia mein guftagu karne se pehlay tumhe sadqat dainay hunge? acha, agar tum aisa nah karo aur Allah ne tum ko is se maaf kar diya to namaz qaim karte raho, zkoh dete raho aur Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte raho tum jo kuch karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
  58,14,"kya tum ne dekha nahi unn logon ko jinhon ne dost banaya hai aik aisay giroh ko jo Allah ka maghzoob hai? woh nah tumahray hain nah unn ke, aur woh jaan boojh kar jhooti baat par kasmain khatay hain"
  58,15,"Allah ne un ke liye sakht azaab muhayya kar rakha hai, barray hi buray kartoot hain jo woh kar rahay hain"
  58,16,"onhon ne apni qasmon ko dhaal bana rakha hai jis ki aarr mein woh Allah ki raah se logon ko roktay hain, iss par un ke liye zillat ka azaab hai"
  58,17,"Allah se bachanay ke liye nah un ke maal kuch kaam ayen ge nah un ki aulaad woh dozakh ke yaar hain, isi mein woh hamesha rahen ge"
  58,18,"jis roz Allah un sab ko uthaye ga, woh is ke samnay bhi usi terhan kasmain khayen ge jis terhan tumahray samnay khatay hain aur apne nazdeek yeh samjhain ge ke is se un ka kuch kaam ban jaye ga khoob jaan lau, woh parlay darjay ke jhutay hain"
  58,19,"shetan unn par musallat ho chuka hai aur a ُs ne khuda ki yaad unn ke dil se bhala di hai woh shetan ki party ke log hain khabardaar ho, shetan ki party walay hi khasaray mein rehne walay hain"
  58,20,yaqeenan zaleel tareen makhloqaat mein se hain woh log jo Allah aur is ke rasool ka muqaabla karte hain
  58,21,Allah ne likh diya hai ke mein aur mere rasool ghalib ho kar rahen ge fi al waqea Allah zabardast aur zor aawar hai
  58,22,"tum kabhi yeh nah pao ge ke jo log Allah aur akhirat par imaan rakhnay walay hain woh unn logon se mohabbat karte hon jinhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat ki hai, khuwa woh unn ke baap hon, ya unn ke betay, ya unn ke bhai ya unn ke ahal khandan yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon mein Allah ne imaan Sabt kar diya hai aur apni taraf se aik rooh ataa kar ke un ko qowat bakhsh hai woh un ko aisijannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi un mein woh hamesha rahen ge Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se raazi hue woh Allah ki party ke log hain khabardaar raho, Allah ki party walay hi Falah panay walay hain"
